"##练习 9.4(1)":[971,986],"##练习 9.4(1)#{1}":[973,986],"##2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算":[987,1124],"##2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算#{1}":[989,1124],"##3 三角形式下复数的乘方与开方":[1125,1168],"##3 三角形式下复数的乘方与开方#{1}":[1127,1168],"##练习 9.4(2)":[1169,1180],"##练习 9.4(2)#{1}":[1171,1180],"##习题 9.4":[1181,1182],"##A 组[3]":[1183,1212],"##A 组[3]#{1}":[1185,1212],"##课后阅读":[1213,1214],"##三次方程求根公式与复数的起源":[1215,1266],"##三次方程求根公式与复数的起源#{1}":[1217,1266],"##内容提要":[1267,1332],"##内容提要#{1}":[1269,1332],"##复习题":[1333,1334],"##A 组[4]":[1335,1412],"##A 组[4]#{1}":[1337,1412],"##拓展与思考":[1413,1417],"##拓展与思考#{1}":[1415,1416],"##拓展与思考#{2}":[1417,1417]},"outlinks":[{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_10_1180_899_236_256_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_10_1180_899_236_256_0.jpg","line":421,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_10_1182_1303_239_407_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_10_1182_1303_239_407_0.jpg","line":427,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","line":443,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","line":447,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","line":471,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","line":485,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","line":641,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","line":897,"embedded":true},{"title":"cos $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}$ sin $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right) \\rbrack$ .\r\n\r\n## 练习 9.4(1)\r\n\r\n1. 下列复数是否用三角形式来表示的? 为什么?\r\n\r\n(1)3π(cos 0.5+i sin 0.5)； (2) $2\\left( {\\sin 1 + \\mathrm{i}\\cos 1}\\right)$ ；\r\n\r\n(3) $\\cos {131\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {131\\pi }$ ； (4) $\\sqrt{2}\\left( {\\cos {0.3\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {0.2\\pi }}\\right)$ ；\r\n\r\n(5) $- 2\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{4} + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{4}}\\right)$ ； (6) $3\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{5} - \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{5}}\\right)$ .\r\n\r\n2. 把下列复数用三角形式表示(用辐角主值):\r\n\r\n(1) 3; (2)-2i;\r\n\r\n(3) $1 + \\mathrm{i}$ ； (4)-1+ $\\sqrt{3}\\mathrm{i}$ .\r\n\r\n## 2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算\r\n\r\n现在我们讨论三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式.\r\n\r\n设有两个用三角形式表示的复数 ${z}_{1} = r\\left( {\\cos \\alpha  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\alpha }\\right)$ 与 ${z}_{2} = s\\left( {\\cos \\beta  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\beta }\\right)$ ,其中 $r = \\left| {z}_{1}\\right|  \\geq  0, s = \\left| {z}_{2}\\right|  \\geq  0$ ,则\r\n\r\nQ\r\n\r\n$$\r\n{z}_{1}{z}_{2} = {rs}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  ;\r\n$$\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\\frac{{z}_{1}}{{z}_{2}} = \\frac{r}{s}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  \\left( {{z}_{2} \\neq  0}\\right) .\r\n$$\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式称为棣莫弗公式.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n![bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","line":969},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","line":1117,"embedded":true}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"fx8ile","at":1773364592277},"key":"03-上海教材md/必修二第9章复数/必修二第9章复数-dollar.md"},
